<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/pages/shop.css">
</head>
<body>

  <%- include("../partials/header") %>

  <main>
    <section class="order-success-section">
      <div class="container order-success-container">
        <div class="order-success-card">
          <div class="success-icon">OK</div>
          <span class="section-tag">Pedido enviado</span>
          <h1>Pedido criado com sucesso</h1>
          <p>Agora pague via Pix, copie a mensagem do pedido e envie no Discord com o comprovante.</p>

          <% if (orderCode) { %>
            <div class="success-order-code">
              <span>Codigo do pedido</span>
              <strong><%= orderCode %></strong>
            </div>
          <% } %>

          <% if (order) { %>
            <div class="success-payment-box">
              <h2>Pagamento via Pix</h2>
              <div class="success-payment-total">
                <span>Valor total</span>
                <strong><%= formatPrice(order.total) %></strong>
              </div>

              <% if (pix && pix.pixCopyPaste) { %>
                <% if (pix.pixQrCode) { %>
                  <div class="pix-qrcode-box">
                    <img src="<%= pix.pixQrCode %>" alt="QR Code Pix do pedido <%= order.code %>">
                  </div>
                <% } %>

                <div class="pix-copy-box">
                  <label for="pixPayload">Pix Copia e Cola</label>
                  <textarea id="pixPayload" readonly><%= pix.pixCopyPaste %></textarea>
                  <button type="button" class="btn-primary pix-copy-btn" id="copyPixButton">Copiar Pix</button>
                </div>

                <% if (pix.pixError) { %>
                  <div class="success-warning"><strong>Aviso Pix:</strong><span><%= pix.pixError %></span></div>
                <% } %>
              <% } else { %>
                <div class="success-warning">
                  <strong>Pix nao configurado:</strong>
                  <span>Entre em contato com a gestao informando o codigo do pedido.</span>
                </div>
              <% } %>
            </div>

            <div class="success-warning">
              <strong>Conferencia obrigatoria:</strong>
              <span>Envie a mensagem copiada e o comprovante. A equipe confere Pix, dados do pedido e liberacao dos beneficios.</span>
            </div>
          <% } %>

          <div class="success-actions">
            <% if (orderCode) { %>
              <button type="button" class="btn-primary success-copy-btn" id="copyOrderCodeButton">Copiar codigo</button>
              <button type="button" class="btn-secondary success-copy-btn" id="copyDiscordMessageButton">Copiar mensagem para Discord</button>
            <% } %>
            <a href="<%= discordInvite %>" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-primary">Abrir Discord</a>
            <a href="/loja/consultar" class="btn-secondary">Consultar pedido</a>
            <a href="/loja" class="btn-secondary">Voltar para loja</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <% if (order) { %>
    <textarea id="discordMessageText" class="success-hidden-copy-text" readonly>
PEDIDO SURVIVALZ - <%= order.code %>

Nick: <%= order.customer.sampNick || order.customer.name || "Nao informado" %>
Discord: <%= order.customer.discord || "Nao informado" %>

Produtos:
<% order.items.forEach((item) => { %>
- <%= item.quantity %>x <%= item.name %> - <%= formatPrice(item.totalCents) %>
<% }) %>

Total: <%= formatPrice(order.total) %>
Cupom: <%= order.coupon || "Nenhum" %>
Status: <%= String(order.status || "pendente").replace(/_/g, " ") %>
Pagamento: <%= order.paymentMethod === "pix" || !order.paymentMethod ? "Pix manual" : order.paymentMethod %>

Aviso: ja realizei ou vou realizar o pagamento via Pix. Favor conferir Pix, comprovante e dados do pedido antes de liberar os beneficios.
    </textarea>

    <textarea id="orderCodeText" class="success-hidden-copy-text" readonly><%= order.code %></textarea>
  <% } %>

  <%- include("../partials/footer") %>
  <script src="/js/pixCopy.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
